            <title>[SOLR-8303] CustomBufferedIndexInput should include resource description when throwing EOFException</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/SOLR-8303</link>
                <project id="12310230" key="SOLR">Solr</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;The other implementations of IndexInput all include the resource description when throwing an EOFException, for example:&lt;br/&gt;
&lt;a href=&quot;https://github.com/apache/lucene-solr/blob/trunk/lucene/core/src/java/org/apache/lucene/store/ByteBufferIndexInput.java#L81&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://github.com/apache/lucene-solr/blob/trunk/lucene/core/src/java/org/apache/lucene/store/ByteBufferIndexInput.java#L81&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;CustomBufferedIndexInput should follow suit.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
